this is an alpha release of 'No password for you' This version is not the final version of this app and it is solely made for debugging purpose only . 
 You should not Enter any sensitive info while using this application or to test the application , as your data can be used for debugging purpose. 
 If you have some problem regarding your data , contact me on my E-mail. 
 Your contribution makes the open source more better , if you find any bug,crash , new features, secuirity leaks , or any other problem, you can submit it on Github issues or on my E-mail. 
 the report must include your device info, steps to reproduce the error, Expected results, Actual result , Visual proof if possible (screenshot , recording , etc.),priority of error. 
Contact me : Rudrapratapsinhchauhan1@gmail.com 
Github: https://github.com/RudraOp9/no-password-for-you
